    metaEn:[['Time','20 min'],['Difficulty','Easy'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','20分钟'],['难度','简单'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>1</strong> whole sea bass (600–700g), cleaned','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> light soy sauce','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> Shaoxing wine','<strong>1 tsp</strong> sugar','<strong>4 slices</strong> fresh ginger','<strong>2</strong> spring onions, julienned','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> neutral oil','<strong>1 tsp</strong> sesame oil'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1条</strong> 鲈鱼（600–700g），处理干净','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 生抽','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 绍兴酒','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 糖','<strong>4片</strong> 新鲜生姜','<strong>2根</strong> 葱，切丝','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 中性油','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 麻油'],
    stepsEn:['Score the fish 3 times on each side. Rub with Shaoxing wine and a pinch of salt. Place ginger slices inside the cavity and under the fish.','Steam over high heat for exactly 8 minutes (for a 600g fish). Do not lift the lid.','While fish steams, mix soy sauce, sugar and 2 tbsp water in a small pan. Heat until sugar dissolves.','Remove fish. Discard any liquid that has collected. Pour the warm soy mixture over the fish.','Scatter spring onion shreds on top. Heat oil until smoking, then pour directly over the onions — they will sizzle dramatically. Drizzle sesame oil. Serve immediately.'],
    stepsZh:['鱼身两面各划3刀，用绍兴酒和少许盐抹匀，姜片放入鱼腹和鱼身下方。','大火蒸恰好8分钟（600g的鱼），中途不要揭盖。','蒸鱼时，生抽、糖和2汤匙水入小锅，加热至糖溶化。','取出鱼，倒掉盘中蒸出的水，将热好的酱汁均匀浇在鱼上。','撒上葱丝。将油烧至冒烟，直接泼在葱丝上——会剧烈冒泡。淋麻油，立即上桌。'],
    notesEn:"The smoking-oil pour is the soul of the dish. It wilts the onion, releases the aroma, and cooks the surface of the fish one final time. Time the steaming precisely — one minute over and the flesh loses its silk.",
    notesZh:'滚油泼葱是这道菜的灵魂。它软化葱丝，激发香气，也为鱼做最后一次加热。蒸的时间要精确——多一分钟，鱼肉就失去了那种丝滑的质感。'
  },
  'recipe-pilaf':{
    emoji:'🍚', eyebrowEn:'Uyghur · Main · 4 servings', eyebrowZh:'维吾尔 · 主菜 · 4人份',
    titleEn:'Lamb Hand-Pulled Rice (Plov)', titleZh:'羊肉手抓饭',
    metaEn:[['Time','1.5h total'],['Difficulty','Medium'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','共1.5小时'],['难度','中等'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>500g</strong> bone-in lamb (shoulder or rib)','<strong>2 cups</strong> long-grain rice, soaked 30 min','<strong>3</strong> large carrots, julienned','<strong>2</strong> onions, sliced','<strong>1 head</strong> garlic, whole','<strong>1 tsp</strong> cumin seeds','<strong>1 tsp</strong> coriander seeds','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> neutral oil','Salt to taste'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>500g</strong> 带骨羊肉（肩部或肋排）','<strong>2杯</strong> 长粒米，提前浸泡30分钟','<strong>3根</strong> 大胡萝卜，切粗丝','<strong>2个</strong> 洋葱，切片','<strong>1头</strong> 大蒜，整头','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 孜然籽','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 香菜籽','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 中性油','盐适量'],
    stepsEn:['Heat oil in a heavy pot (ideally a kazan) over high heat. Brown lamb pieces until deep golden. Remove.','In the same pot, fry onions until caramelized. Add carrots and cook until softened.','Return lamb. Add cumin, coriander, salt and enough boiling water to just cover. Simmer 40 min.','Drain rice and spread evenly over the meat and vegetables. Do not stir. Press the whole garlic head into the center.','Add boiling water to cover rice by 1cm. Cover tightly. Cook on low heat 25–30 min until rice has absorbed all liquid.','Remove garlic. Stir from the bottom to mix. Eat with your hands — that is the correct way.'],
    stepsZh:['大火热油（最好用卡赞锅），将羊肉煎至深金黄色，取出备用。','同一口锅炒洋葱至焦糖化，加入胡萝卜翻炒至软。','放回羊肉，加孜然籽、香菜籽、盐和足量沸水刚好没过食材，小火焖煮40分钟。','沥干米，均匀铺在肉和蔬菜上方，不要翻搅，将整头大蒜插入中央。','加沸水至高出米面约1厘米，盖紧锅盖，小火焖25-30分钟至米饭吸干水分。','取出大蒜，从锅底翻拌均匀，用手抓着吃——这才是正确的方式。'],
    notesEn:"The layering is the technique — meat and vegetables on the bottom, rice on top, steam doing the work. The garlic becomes impossibly sweet and mild after steaming. The correct vessel is a kazan, but a Dutch oven works.",
    notesZh:'分层是关键技术——肉和蔬菜在下，米饭在上，靠蒸汽完成一切。大蒜经过蒸制后变得极度甘甜温和。正确的容器是卡赞锅，但铸铁锅也可以。'
  },
  'recipe-roastduck':{
    emoji:'🦆', eyebrowEn:'Beijing · Main · 4 servings', eyebrowZh:'京式 · 主菜 · 4人份',
