    metaEn:[['Time','Overnight + 2h'],['Difficulty','Advanced'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','隔夜 + 2小时'],['难度','高级'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>1</strong> whole duck (2–2.5kg)','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> honey','<strong>2 tbsp</strong> soy sauce','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> Shaoxing wine','<strong>1 tsp</strong> five-spice powder','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> maltose (or extra honey)','<strong>2 tbsp</strong> rice vinegar','Hoisin sauce, spring onion, cucumber, thin pancakes — for serving'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1只</strong> 整鸭（2–2.5kg）','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 蜂蜜','<strong>2汤匙</strong> 生抽','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 绍兴酒','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 五香粉','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 麦芽糖（或额外蜂蜜）','<strong>2汤匙</strong> 米醋','甜面酱、葱丝、黄瓜条、薄饼——配餐用'],
    stepsEn:['Blanch the whole duck in boiling water 2 min. Pat completely dry. Mix honey, maltose, rice vinegar — brush all over the duck. Air-dry uncovered in the fridge overnight (minimum 12h). The skin must be completely dry.','Remove from fridge 1 hour before cooking. Preheat oven to 200°C.','Mix soy sauce, Shaoxing wine and five-spice. Brush inside the cavity. Truss the duck with the cavity sealed.','Place breast-side up on a rack over a roasting tray. Roast 30 min, then reduce to 180°C and roast another 60–75 min, basting with honey every 20 min.','Rest 15 min. Carve in thin slices — skin and meat together. Serve with pancakes, hoisin, spring onion and cucumber.'],
    stepsZh:['整鸭放入沸水焯2分钟，完全拍干。将蜂蜜、麦芽糖、米醋混合，刷遍全鸭，不加盖放入冰箱风干隔夜（至少12小时），鸭皮必须完全干燥。','烹制前1小时从冰箱取出，预热烤箱至200°C。','生抽、绍兴酒、五香粉混合，刷在鸭腹内，将鸭腹开口封住并绑好。','鸭胸朝上放烤架，下垫烤盘，烤30分钟后降至180°C再烤60-75分钟，每20分钟刷一次蜂蜜。','静置15分钟，片成薄片——皮肉一起，配薄饼、甜面酱、葱丝和黄瓜条食用。'],
    notesEn:"The overnight air-dry is non-negotiable. Moisture is the enemy of crispy skin. The basting creates the lacquered finish. If you have a bicycle pump, inflate the skin from the neck before air-drying — it separates skin from fat and is worth the effort.",
    notesZh:'隔夜风干不可省略，水分是脆皮的敌人。反复刷蜜制造漆亮表皮。如果有打气筒，风干前从颈部给鸭皮充气——这能将皮与脂肪分离，值得那点麻烦。'
  },
  'recipe-lambchops':{
    emoji:'🍖', eyebrowEn:'Xinjiang · Main · 2 servings', eyebrowZh:'新疆 · 主菜 · 2人份',
