    metaEn:[['Time','30 min + marinate'],['Difficulty','Easy'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','30分钟 + 腌制'],['难度','简单'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>8</strong> lamb rib chops','<strong>2 tbsp</strong> ground cumin','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> chili flakes','<strong>1 tsp</strong> Sichuan peppercorn, ground','<strong>1 tsp</strong> coarse salt','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> neutral oil'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>8根</strong> 羊肋排','<strong>2汤匙</strong> 孜然粉','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 辣椒碎','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 花椒粉','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 粗盐','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 中性油'],
    stepsEn:['Pat lamb chops dry. Mix cumin, chili flakes, Sichuan pepper and salt. Rub generously all over the chops. Marinate at room temperature 30 min minimum.','Heat a cast-iron grill pan or outdoor grill until smoking hot.','Brush chops lightly with oil. Grill 3–4 min per side for medium (adjust for thickness). Do not move them once placed — let the crust form.','Rest 5 min. Finish with a final dusting of cumin and chili before serving.'],
    stepsZh:['羊排拍干，将孜然、辣椒碎、花椒和盐混合，大量涂抹在羊排上，室温腌制至少30分钟。','铸铁烤盘或户外烤架烧至冒烟热。','羊排刷少量油，每面烤3-4分钟至五分熟（根据厚度调整），放上后不要移动——等待焦壳形成。','静置5分钟，上桌前再撒一层孜然和辣椒碎。'],
    notesEn:"The simplicity is the point. Xinjiang lamb needs nothing but heat, cumin and chili. Any further intervention is a mistake. The smoke is essential — do not attempt this on a low flame.",
    notesZh:'简单本身就是意义。新疆羊肉只需要高温、孜然和辣椒。任何多余的干预都是错误。烟熏气不可缺少——不要在小火上做这道菜。'
  },
  'recipe-handlamb':{
    emoji:'🥩', eyebrowEn:'Mongolian · Main · 4 servings', eyebrowZh:'蒙古 · 主菜 · 4人份',
