    ingrEn:['<strong>1.5kg</strong> bone-in lamb (shoulder or leg)','<strong>1</strong> onion, halved','<strong>4 slices</strong> ginger','<strong>2</strong> star anise','<strong>1 tsp</strong> whole Sichuan peppercorns','<strong>2 tbsp</strong> Shaoxing wine','Salt to taste','For dipping: minced garlic, black vinegar, chili oil, fresh coriander'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1.5kg</strong> 带骨羊肉（肩部或腿部）','<strong>1个</strong> 洋葱，对半切','<strong>4片</strong> 生姜','<strong>2颗</strong> 八角','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 整粒花椒','<strong>2汤匙</strong> 绍兴酒','盐适量','蘸料：蒜末、黑醋、辣椒油、香菜'],
    stepsEn:['Place lamb in a pot of cold water. Bring to a boil, cook 5 min, then discard the water. Rinse the lamb and the pot.','Return lamb to the clean pot. Add onion, ginger, star anise, Sichuan peppercorns, Shaoxing wine and enough cold water to cover by 5cm.','Bring to a boil, skim any foam, then reduce to a steady simmer. Cook 1.5–2 hours until the meat pulls easily from the bone.','Remove lamb and let rest 10 min. Pull the meat with your hands into large chunks — this is deliberate, not lazy. Bones come out naturally.','Serve immediately with dipping sauce. The broth is for drinking alongside.'],
    stepsZh:['羊肉冷水下锅，煮沸5分钟后倒掉水，冲洗羊肉和锅。','羊肉放回清锅，加洋葱、姜片、八角、花椒、绍兴酒和足量冷水，超过羊肉5厘米。','大火烧开，撇净浮沫，转中小火保持稳定沸腾，煮1.5-2小时至肉可轻松离骨。','取出羊肉，静置10分钟，用手将肉撕成大块——这是刻意为之，不是懒惰，骨头自然脱出。','立即上桌，配蘸料食用，汤可以随餐喝。'],
    notesEn:"The point of hand-pulling is texture — the meat tears along its natural grain, which no knife can replicate. The broth, strained and salted, is one of the finest things you can drink.",
    notesZh:'徒手撕肉的意义在于质感——肉沿自然纹理撕裂，这是刀切无法复制的。将汤过滤后加盐，是你能喝到的最好的东西之一。'
  },
  'recipe-mouthwater':{
    emoji:'🍗', eyebrowEn:'Sichuan · Cold Dish · 3 servings', eyebrowZh:'川味 · 凉菜 · 3人份',
    titleEn:'Mouthwatering Chicken', titleZh:'口水鸡',
    metaEn:[['Time','45 min'],['Difficulty','Easy–Medium'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','45分钟'],['难度','简单-中等'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>1</strong> whole chicken (or 4 bone-in thighs)','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> Sichuan chili oil','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> sesame paste','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> soy sauce','<strong>1 tbsp</strong> black vinegar','<strong>1 tsp</strong> Sichuan peppercorn oil','<strong>1 tsp</strong> sugar','<strong>2 cloves</strong> garlic, minced','<strong>1 tsp</strong> ginger, minced','Toasted sesame seeds, spring onion, coriander to finish'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1只</strong> 整鸡（或4块带骨鸡腿）','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 四川辣椒油','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 芝麻酱','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 生抽','<strong>1汤匙</strong> 黑醋','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 花椒油','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 糖','<strong>2瓣</strong> 蒜，剁末','<strong>1茶匙</strong> 生姜末','熟芝麻、葱花、香菜收尾'],
    stepsEn:['Bring a large pot of water to a boil with ginger and spring onion. Add chicken. When it returns to a boil, reduce to the lowest possible simmer. Poach 20–25 min — the water should barely move.','Remove chicken and immediately submerge in ice water for 10 min. This gives the skin its characteristic silky texture.','While chicken chills, whisk together chili oil, sesame paste, soy sauce, vinegar, peppercorn oil, sugar, garlic and ginger. Taste — it should be spicy, numbing, sour and slightly sweet simultaneously.','Chop chicken through the bone into bite-sized pieces. Arrange on a plate. Pour sauce generously over. Finish with sesame seeds, spring onion and coriander.'],
    stepsZh:['大锅加水，放姜片和葱段，大火烧开。放入鸡，再次沸腾后转至最小火，保持几乎不动的水温，焖煮20-25分钟。','取出鸡，立即放入冰水中浸泡10分钟——这赋予鸡皮标志性的爽滑质感。','鸡浸冰水时，将辣椒油、芝麻酱、生抽、醋、花椒油、糖、蒜末和姜末调匀。品尝——应该同时辣、麻、酸、微甜。','鸡带骨斩成小块，摆盘，大量浇上酱汁，撒芝麻、葱花和香菜收尾。'],
    notesEn:"The ice bath is not optional — it is what makes this dish. The contrast between the warm sauce and the cold chicken, the numbing pepper and the bright vinegar, the silk of the skin and the richness of the sesame — this dish is about contrast.",
    notesZh:'冰水浴不可省略——这正是这道菜的精髓。温热酱汁与冰凉鸡肉的对比，花椒的麻与醋的爽的对比，鸡皮的爽滑与芝麻酱的浓郁的对比——这道菜的一切都关乎对比。'
  },
  'recipe-steak':{
