    titleEn:'Pan-Seared Steak', titleZh:'干煎牛排',
    metaEn:[['Time','20 min'],['Difficulty','Easy'],['Rating','★★★★★']],
    metaZh:[['时间','20分钟'],['难度','简单'],['评分','★★★★★']],
    ingrEn:['<strong>1</strong> ribeye or NY strip (2.5–3cm thick)','<strong>2 tbsp</strong> neutral oil','<strong>3 tbsp</strong> unsalted butter','<strong>3 cloves</strong> garlic, crushed','<strong>3 sprigs</strong> thyme or rosemary','Coarse salt and black pepper'],
    ingrZh:['<strong>1块</strong> 肋眼或纽约客（2.5–3cm厚）','<strong>2汤匙</strong> 中性油','<strong>3汤匙</strong> 无盐黄油','<strong>3瓣</strong> 大蒜，拍碎','<strong>3枝</strong> 百里香或迷迭香','粗盐和黑胡椒'],
    stepsEn:['Remove steak from fridge 45 min before cooking. Pat completely dry. Season aggressively with salt and pepper on all surfaces — more than you think is needed.','Heat a cast-iron pan over highest heat until smoking. Add oil. Place steak — it should scream when it hits the pan.','Cook 2 min without moving. Flip. Cook 2 min. Then flip every 30 seconds for a final 2 min, building the crust.','Add butter, garlic and herbs. Tilt the pan and baste the steak continuously with the foaming butter for 1 min.','Rest on a wire rack 5–8 min. This is mandatory, not optional. Cut against the grain.'],
    stepsZh:['牛排从冰箱取出后在室温放置45分钟，完全拍干，各面大量撒盐和黑胡椒——比你以为需要的要多。','铸铁锅大火烧至冒烟，下油，放入牛排——下锅时应该发出响亮的嘶嘶声。','不移动煎2分钟，翻面，再煎2分钟，最后每隔30秒翻面共2分钟，积累焦壳。','加黄油、大蒜和香草，倾斜锅身，用起泡的黄油不停淋制牛排约1分钟。','放在烤架上静置5-8分钟，这是必须的而非可选的。逆纹切开。'],
    notesEn:"Dry surface, ripping-hot pan, aggressive seasoning, proper rest. Every step has a reason. The resting allows the juices to redistribute — cut too early and they run out onto the board, not into your mouth.",
    notesZh:'干燥表面、极热铸铁锅、大量调味、充分静置。每一步都有其理由。静置让肉汁重新分布——切得太早，肉汁流到砧板上，而不是流进你口中。'
  },
  'recipe-hunanbelly':{
